            "reviews": "“Quite simply this is the most technically accurate <strong>sailing simulator</strong> I have experienced. This alone can teach you all the jargon, the procedures and best practices for real life sailing. Excellent A*”<br>A* – <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/curators/curatorsreviewing/?appid=794860\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Sim UK</a><br><br>“Have you ever wanted to own a sail boat but could never afford one? Here is your chance to experience awesome world of sailing. Awesome graphics and game play. 1000s of hours of fun!”<br><a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/curator/32668148-Games-without-Borders\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Games without Borders</a><br><br>“As well as being a great learning tool, and great reminder for skippers and crew who only get occasional opportunities to sail, it's great fun in its own right and provides the opportunity to get a sailing 'fix' whenever you have a spare 15-20 minutes.”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.esailyachtsimulator.com/blog/practical-boat-owner-esail-compelling\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Practical Boat Owner</a><br>",
